# TECH STACK
- TypeScript, Next.js (App Router), Tailwind CSS.
- Use functional components and React Hooks.

# CODING STANDARDS
- Use 'const' for function definitions.
- strictly type all variables and functions (no 'any').
- Use Tailwind for styling (avoid inline styles).
- File structure: Group related components in feature folders.
- Prefer server components where possible (if using Next.js).
